titleInfo.title: (PC) Brown v. Swan et al
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER signed by Magistrate Judge John F. Moulds on 1/3/13 ORDERING that within 15 days from the date of this order plaintiff shall inform the court in writing whether he still seeks voluntary dismissal of this action or, instead, whether he wants to withdraw his September 10, 2012 motion for voluntary dismissal. Failure to respond to this order will result in a recommendation that this action be dismissed without prejudice. Plaintiffs November 9, 2012 motion for extension of time 43 is DENIED without prejudice. Plaintiffs November 21, 2012 motion for preliminary injunction and/or temporary restraining order 44 is DENIED without prejudice. Plaintiffs December 12, 2012 motion for temporary restraining order 45 is DENIED without prejudice.(Dillon, M)
